						<summary>

						<p>On a rock called Anantabaṇḍa about 1(1/2) miles from the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Siddhārthi, Āshāḍha, śu. 2, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of some lands at Dēvaram to the god Narasiṁha of Nagnērukallu by Kaṭēpalli Malnēniṅgāru.</p>						

